Title: Relates to the registration of new curricula or programs of study offered by a not-for-profit college or university
Summary: Relates to the registration of new curricula or programs of study offered by a not-for-profit college or university; provides for the procedures to have such curricula or programs of study approved by the department of education.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the registration of new curricula or programs of study offered by a not-for-profit college or university
